<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٧٦ ... سُورَةُ الإِنْسَانِ ... آياتها ٣١ مدنية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هَلْ أَتَى}</span> ... قَدْ مَضَى.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حِينٌ}</span> ... زَمَنٌ طَوِيلٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَمْشَاجٍ}</span> ... مُخْتَلِطَةٍ مِنْ مَاءِ الرَّجُلِ وَمَاءِ المَرْأَةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَّبْتَلِيهِ}</span> ... نَخْتَبِرُهُ بِالأَوَامِرِ، وَالنَّوَاهِي.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هَدَيْنَاهُ السَّبِيلَ}</span> ... بَيَّنَّا لَهُ طَرِيقَ الخَيْرِ، وَالشَّرِّ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَلَاسِلَا}</span> ... قُيُودًا مِنْ حَدِيدٍ تُشَدُّ بِهَا أَرْجُلُهُمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَغْلَالًا}</span> ... تُغَلُّ وَتُجْمَعُ بِهَا أَيْدِيهِمْ إِلَى أَعْنَاقِهِمْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَسَعِيرًا}</span> ... نَارًا يُحْرَقُونَ بِهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَاسٍ}</span> ... إِنَاءِ شُرْبِ الخَمْرِ، وَفِيهَا خَمْرٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِزَاجُهَا كَافُورًا}</span> ... مَخْلُوطَةً بِأَحْسَنِ أَنْوَاعِ الطِّيبِ، وَهُوَ مَاءُ الكَافُورِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَشْرَبُ بِهَا}</span> ... يَشْرَبُونَ مُتَلَذِّذِينَ بِهَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُفَجِّرُونَهَا}</span> ... يُجْرُونَهَا إِجْرَاءً سَهْلًا حَيْثُ شَاؤُوا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالنَّذْرِ}</span> ... بِمَا أَوْجَبُوا عَلَى أَنْفُسِهِمْ مِنَ الطَّاعَاتِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُسْتَطِيرًا}</span> ... فَاشِيًا مُنْتَشِرًا عَلَى النَّاسِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيَتِيمًا}</span> ... طِفْلًا مَاتَ وَالِدُهُ قَبْلَ بُلُوغِهِ، وَلَا مَالَ لَهُ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَسِيرًا}</span> ... المَاخُوذَ فِي الحَرْبِ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>